    "name": "Dustwind: Resistance",
    "steam_appid": 3110370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《尘风：抵抗》是一款设定在末日后的战术单人游戏，融合实时战斗与暂停规划机制。率领小队对抗入侵军队，做出艰难战术抉择，不惜一切代价守护人民与生活方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >领导抵抗军</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/028c0c67b2b032dc29298f5ee6e110f8.poster.avif?t=1769780479\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/028c0c67b2b032dc29298f5ee6e110f8.webm?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/028c0c67b2b032dc29298f5ee6e110f8.mp4?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥杰克、他的小队及忠犬迪塞尔。夺回家园，给劫掠者致命一击。为自由而战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >暂停·谋略·行动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/396a6c64c996fcb9f68aff1317733efa.poster.avif?t=1769780479\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/396a6c64c996fcb9f68aff1317733efa.webm?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/396a6c64c996fcb9f68aff1317733efa.mp4?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗实时展开，但你可随时暂停下达指令，将混乱化为掌控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战术抉择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/8b76b011f64953474cc7929cb968cbc6.poster.avif?t=1769780479\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/8b76b011f64953474cc7929cb968cbc6.webm?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/8b76b011f64953474cc7929cb968cbc6.mp4?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蛮力突击、潜行暗杀、阵地布防、时机把握、精准狙击——战斗方式由你掌控。但切记：敌人绝非等闲之辈，任何失误都可能招致灭顶之灾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >塑造角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/8cffce6e1b0aa85c909fb11366113fd4.poster.avif?t=1769780479\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/8cffce6e1b0aa85c909fb11366113fd4.webm?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/8cffce6e1b0aa85c909fb11366113fd4.mp4?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过全新升级的角色系统培养小队。选择最契合战术风格的技能与装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >善用战争工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/2c2cb05936ef188a17844db295156464.poster.avif?t=1769780479\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/2c2cb05936ef188a17844db295156464.webm?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/2c2cb05936ef188a17844db295156464.mp4?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射击、砍杀、踢击或撕咬。布设陷阱、投掷手雷、部署机枪塔与路障，甚至驾驶装甲车碾压敌人。杀戮方式层出不穷，死亡方式同样多样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自创战场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/6daccfbef50383cd2bdad0c11ad94b05.poster.avif?t=1769780479\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/6daccfbef50383cd2bdad0c11ad94b05.webm?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110370/extras/6daccfbef50383cd2bdad0c11ad94b05.mp4?t=1769780479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过内置地图编辑器打造专属地图与战役，直接分享至Steam创意工坊延续战斗激情。</p>",
